nodes.text: Cantina Roll-Call: Shedding Light on Some Alien Aliases

Cantina Roll-Call: Shedding Light on Some Alien Aliases is an article appearing on the StarWars.com website. It reveals the behind-the-scenes details of the aliens and other characters who appear in the cantina scene of Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. The article was written by Pablo Hidalgo and published on Octuber 27, 2008.
